msgstr "%{hero} ha sido derrotado y no aparecerá en escenarios posteriores."

msgid "The dwarves recognize their allies and gladly join your forces."
msgstr "Los enanos reconocen a sus aliados y se unen con gusto a tus fuerzas."

msgid "The ogres recognize you as the Dwarfbane and lumber over to join you."
msgstr ""
"Los ogros te reconocen como el Mataenanos y acuden a unirse a tus filas."

msgid ""
"The dragons, snarling and growling, agree to join forces with you, their "
"'Ally'."
msgstr ""
"Los dragones, gruñendo y rugiendo, aceptan unir fuerzas contigo, su 'aliado'."

msgid ""
"As you approach the group of elves, their leader calls them all to "
"attention. He shouts to them, \"Who of you is brave enough to join this "
"fearless ally of ours?\" The group explodes with cheers as they run to join "
"your ranks."
msgstr ""
"Al acercarte al grupo de elfos, su líder los llama a todos a la posición de "
"firmes. Les grita: \"¿Quién de vosotros es lo suficientemente valiente como "
"para unirse a este intrépido aliado nuestro?\". El grupo estalla en vítores "
"y corre a unirse a tus filas."

msgid ""
"The dwarves hail you, \"Any friend of Roland is a friend of ours. You may "
"pass.\""
msgstr ""
"Los enanos te saludan: \"Cualquier amigo de Roland es amigo nuestro. Puedes "
"pasar.\""

msgid ""
"The ogres give you a grunt of recognition, \"Archibald's allies may pass.\""
msgstr ""
"Los ogros emiten un gruñido de reconocimiento: \"Los aliados de Archibald "
"pueden pasar\"."

msgid ""
"The dragons see you and call out. \"Our alliance with Archibald compels us "
"to join you. Unfortunately you have no room. A pity!\" They quickly scatter."
msgstr ""
"Los dragones te ven y gritan: \"Nuestra alianza con Archibald nos obliga a "
"unirnos a vosotros. Lamentablemente, no tenéis sitio. ¡Qué lástima!\". Se "
"dispersan rápidamente."

msgid ""
"The elves stand at attention as you approach. Their leader calls to you and "
"says, \"Let us not impede your progress, ally! Move on, and may victory be "
"yours.\""
msgstr ""
"Los elfos se ponen firmes a tu paso. Su líder te llama y te dice: \"¡No "
"impidamos tu avance, aliado! Sigue adelante, y que la victoria sea tuya\"."

msgid "\"The Dwarfbane!!!!, run for your lives.\""
msgstr "\"¡¡¡El Mataenanos!!!! ¡Corran por sus vidas!\""

