"The Moat slows and weakens attacking units. Any walking unit entering the "
"moat must end its turn there and can only move within the moat one hex at a "
"time. Any creature present in the moat will have its defense skill reduced "
"by %{count}."
msgstr ""
"El foso ralentiza y debilita a las unidades atacantes. Cualquier unidad que "
"entre en el foso debe terminar su turno allí y solo puede moverse dentro del "
"foso un hexágono. Cualquier criatura presente en el foso verá reducida su "
"defensa en %{count}."

